Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:05.680 --> 00:00:09.109
P3 is a medium size 
fresh pasta machine

00:00:09.109 --> 00:00:12.929
it's suitable for restaurants and delis

00:00:12.929 --> 00:00:18.019
P3 can knead up to 3 Kg of flour per time
with a production potential

00:00:18.019 --> 00:00:22.489
up to 8-10 kg/h

00:00:22.489 --> 00:00:28.269
P3 can knead all flour types

00:00:28.269 --> 00:00:40.010
it has fans that allows a preliminary
drying of the product

00:00:54.400 --> 00:00:58.460
is equipped with a rotating
single blade knife

00:00:58.460 --> 00:01:05.560
or with 2 or 4 blades to get
types of very short pasta

00:01:05.750 --> 00:01:09.750
P3 is entirely made of stainless steel

00:01:09.750 --> 00:01:13.240
strong, automatic and very reliable

00:01:13.240 --> 00:01:20.240
it can be easily disassembled and cleaned

00:01:26.190 --> 00:01:33.190
P3 produces pasta sheets in double stripes

00:01:40.780 --> 00:01:47.780
the thickness of the sheet is adjustable

00:01:48.770 --> 00:01:51.740
pasta sheet stripes, are arranged
on a flat surface

00:01:51.740 --> 00:01:58.740
and can be rolled on special cylinders

00:01:59.180 --> 00:02:06.180
on the back of the machine is mounted
a semi-automatic "ravioli" unit

00:02:21.759 --> 00:02:28.759
the "ravioli" unit can support 
all types of filling

00:02:35.709 --> 00:02:40.900
and produces rustic ravioli format
34 x 40 mm

